description:
sonic the hedgehog and his family heard to the beach for another day of fun, but things don't go as planned when they run into Robotnik and his bounty hunters, sleet and dingo arrive and challenge the crew to a sand castle building competition. Who will win and who will lose.

This is a bonus episode to my last video, "Bartleby Teaches His Lover Sonic How To Swim" which can be found, here.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MmkP_ZK7yTM
